_sText:
------------Aim_4Bunkers------------


Map name: aim_4bunkers

author: Swij

Description: This is a aim map with basicly 4 bunkers
on a flat surface , but you can go beneath the surface too :D.
You spawn with colt if your a ct and with a ak if your a T, inside
the bunker there's two augs and one scout, in the middle there's a 
m249 and some nades, to get to the secret room you'll have to find 
the right place to climb up and then you just have to simply walk 
to the room entrance.

How to install: Just move the "Maps" (that you got in this .Rar) to your

Steam/steamapps/ACCOUNTNAME/counter-strike source/cstrike



it should look like this:
Steam/steamapps/ACCOUNTNAME/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps

in the maps folder you'll find aim_4bunkers.bsp and aim_4bunkers.nav
if you have done  it right.

Credits:

Swij (made the pack)

and the 7 bots that Beta tested it -.-
